text: Maleic anhydride is an organic compound with the chemical formula . It is the acid anhydride of maleic acid. Maleic anhydride is used to make some plastics. == Chemistry == Maleic acid is a dienophile, a type of chemical used in the Diels-Alder reaction with dienes.
